      "description": "**This spell** prevents any dragon who fails its saving throw from entering the area of effect.\n\nThe spell affects a cubic area whose sides equal the caster's level times 5 feet; thus, a 16th-level caster could affect a cube whose sides each equal 80 feet.\n\nThe dragon can cast spells, blast breath weapon, or hurl missiles (if possible) into the area of effect.\n\nDragons within the area of effect when the spell is cast are not affected.\n\nIf such dragons leave the area of effect, they must succeed a saving throw to reenter the area.\n\nThe material components are the priest's holy symbol and a dragon scale.\n\nThe spell's effectiveness can be greatly increased with the casting of a focus spell.",
