      "description": "Bestows magical flight upon the touched creature.\n\n- Speed: **18** (half if ascending, double when diving).\n- Maneuverability class: **B**.\n- The caster can hover or fly slowly (speed 3) to cast spells.\n- The spell **lasts 1 turn/level + 1d6 turns**, but the caster **does not know** the exact time.\n- DM secretly determines duration.\n\n**Material component**: A **wing feather** from any bird.",
      "source": "Player's Handbook",
