      "casting_time": "2 rds.",
      "duration": "Permanent",
      "save": "None",
      "damage": "",
      "description": "This powerful version of *permanency* allows magical effects to be made **permanent** upon objects or creatures.\n\n- Must follow casting of a compatible spell.\n- Each use **reduces the caster's Constitution by 1 point**.\n- Effects can only be **dispelled by a caster of higher level**.\n\n**Spells usable on the caster only**:\n*comprehend languages, detect evil, detect invisibility, detect magic, infravision, protection from cantrips, protection from evil, protection from normal missiles, read magic, tongues, unseen servant.*\n\n**Spells usable on objects or areas**:\n*enlarge, fear, gust of wind, invisibility, magic mouth, prismatic sphere, stinking cloud, wall of fire, wall of force, web.*\n\n**Spells for objects/areas only**:\n*alarm, audible glamer, dancing lights, distance distortion, solid fog, teleport, wall of fire.*\n\nPermanency may fail after 1,000 years. Other spells may be researched for use, subject to DM approval.",
