      "description": "This potent spell replaces the caster’s heart with a **perfectly crafted stone heart**, changing the caster’s body and essence.\n\n- The caster gains immunity to **nonmagical diseases**, **poison**, **charm**, and **fear**.\n- The caster becomes **undetectable by spells that detect life or emotions**.\n- The transformation is **irreversible** by normal means.\n\nIf the stone heart is **damaged or destroyed**, the caster **dies instantly**.\n\nMaterial component: **the crafted stone heart**, which must be prepared in advance.",
