      "description": "Forces a creature or object to **sink into the earth** or floor it stands upon.\n\n- Requires chanting for the full round.\n- Affected target must make a **save vs. spell** (creature) or **disintegration** (magic item) or become **anchored**.\n\n- If the caster **ceases**, effect ends in 4 turns.\n- If continued, the subject **sinks over the round** in quarters:\n  1. Before initiative, ¼ height.\n  2. After first group, another ¼.\n  3. After second group, another ¼.\n  4. End of round: fully submerged.\n\nThis entombment places the subject in **suspended animation**, ceasing bodily functions.\n**Detect magic** reveals a faint aura. Spells like **freedom**, **dig**, or **transmute rock to mud** may recover the subject.",
