      "save": "None",
      "damage": "",
      "description": "Projects the caster’s **astral body** into the **Astral Plane**, leaving the physical body behind in **suspended animation**.\n\n- Only **magical items** may accompany the caster.\n- Astral travel allows movement to the **Outer Planes** or within the **Prime Material Plane**.\n- Only **one body** can be formed on a plane.\n- **Silvery cord** connects the astral and physical bodies. If broken, the caster **dies**.\n- The caster may bring **up to 7 companions**, joined in a circle.\n\nThe spell lasts until the caster ends it or it's **dispelled** or disrupted. Magic items may be **nonfunctional** in distant planes, with exceptions for powerful artifacts.",
