      "description": "This aura of **life-draining darkness** surrounds the caster and functions both **offensively and defensively**.\n\n- **Offensive use**: Touch attack forces save vs. death magic **at –4**. On fail, victim loses **20% of current HP per round** for 5 rounds.\n- **Defensive use**: Anyone who touches or strikes the caster must save or suffer the same effect (no penalty).\n\nSpell ends when:\n- Caster affects or is attacked by a number of creatures = caster level\n- Duration ends (2 rounds/level)\n- Caster dies or *dispel magic* is used\n\n**Undead are immune**, and **gain 1 HD** if affected, potentially harming the caster.\n\n**Components**: Crushed black opal & diamond (5,000 gp), dust from corporeal undead tied to the Negative Material Plane, and smoky quartz【127:10†TSR 2151 - The Complete Book of Necromancers.pdf】.",
