      "aoe": "One spell-casting creature",
      "casting_time": "1 round",
      "duration": "5 rounds",
      "save": "None",
      "damage": "",
      "description": "This spell allows the recipient to cast spells with **verbal components silently**. The recipient can do so only **within the duration** of vocalize.\n\nIt is useful for stealth or countering effects like *silence*. Vocalize does **not negate silence**, but allows the caster to cast spells normally. **Audible spell effects are still masked** while under silence. Vocalize does **not affect normal speech**.",
