      "duration": "1 round/level",
      "save": "None",
      "damage": "1d6+4 vs undead, 1d6+1 vs others",
      "description": "This spell enchants a bone, turning it into a magical club:\n\n- Acts as a **+4 weapon vs. undead**, dealing **1d6+4 damage**\n- Acts as a **+1 weapon vs. others**, dealing **1d6+1 damage**\n\nUsable only on bones that could be wielded as clubs (e.g., a femur, but not a skull). At the end of the spell, the bone reverts to normal.\n\nIf using weapon proficiencies, **club proficiency applies** to bone clubs. Non-proficient users suffer standard non-proficiency penalties.",
