      "range": "30 yards",
      "aoe": "One creature",
      "casting_time": "1 round",
      "duration": "1 turn/level",
      "save": "None",
      "damage": "",
      "description": "Allows the recipient to continue functioning after reaching 0 hit points. The subject:\n\n- Can act normally until reaching **–10 hp**\n- Suffers **–2 penalty** to attack and saving throws\n- Movement is **halved** once at 0 hp\n\nIf the spell ends before the subject reaches –10 hp, they **die instantly**. If they reach –10 hp, they also die. Normal *raise dead* spells work after death from this effect.",
